https://www.standard.co.uk/news/world/ukraine-brovary-kyiv-tank-battle-russia-putin-war-b987233.html</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/okDOMUj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CardeasIV]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I was sure watching for it..</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DHc111T</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VMn0O4i.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DHc111T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BStev]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>$200 for a service call to fix my dishwasher? I think NOT.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kZKeXXD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/H06vi52.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h501Snu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/izWeA7n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yesterday I put my dishwasher through a self-clean cycle & opened it to find the bottom was filled with water. Called around & turns out 1) repair-people *hate* fixing Bosch dishwashers & 2) the one place that *would* fix it wanted to charge $200 for it - I bought it used for less than that 3 years ago!

My wife & I settled on buying a new one but I kept digging online because a new dishwasher is $$$

& then I pulled off the bottom panel & looked inside. I put the new part in my cart & pulled the old one free only to find the drain pump was jammed by butcher’s twine which must have been stuck in the bottom of a Tupperware or something. Cleaned the spindle & put it back in & it’s FIXED! For free!

Very proud of myself!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kZKeXXD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[StevenAlleyn]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>IMGUR NEEDS AN OPSEC BRIEF.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xUlDwnu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IAzbTEe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Do not post pics about troop movements, locations, dates, numbers of troops and equpt. 

PLEASE

Russia and the enemy can look and see details in photos and conversations that put ukrainias and freedom fighters in danger. 

They can get geolocations, meta data, facial recognition, and info from photos that you may have never considered. 

Your pic alone might not be enough but the enemy has lots of info and can use your pic to solve a puzzle. 

You might think "sauce" on a cool pic or story is nice but so does the enemy. 

You might think a simple pic of a "tank" or group of guys without other info is harmless but the enemy can see other photos and comments and piece things together. 

ALSO IT DOESNT MATTER IF THE PIC IS OLD OR FROM ANOTHER SITE, ITS STILL SPREADING VALUABLE INFO THE ENEMY CAN FIND AND USE. 

DONT LET IMGUR HELP RUSSIA AND HURT OUR FORCES. 

Please stop helping Russia guys! 

Ask yourself before posting... could this help putin find/hunt/kill/or workaround ukrainian forces?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e5rs1Uo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OvRRti9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kpzEKgv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xzcaRw3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jCtcgJq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xUlDwnu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[icutyouinyoursleep]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Just ugh.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/eZy0XXI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ajXbpfP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So I've been having a really nice time getting to know this young lady, and things seemed to be going quite well. But then the word policing began...

I said "things are kinda crazy at work."

Apparently, crazy is a bad word because it's offensive to the neurodivergent, and I'm not allowed to use it regardless of the context having nothing to do with it being used as a slight against anyone.

I said "I appreciate a partner who is intelligent and capable."

Apparently, capable is a bad word because it's offensive to the disabled, and I'm not allowed to use it regardless of the context having nothing to do with it being used as a slight against anyone.

There were more like this, and it just got to the point where it's so exhausting trying to police completely innocent words that I just can't be fucking bothered dealing with this person. I understand that certain words can be harmful, and I try my best to be considerate and thoughtful, but for fucks sakes, relax, lady. 

Yeesh.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eZy0XXI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HomeDepotAisle15]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Edgy, but not completely inaccurate</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DBZQg6F</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3xIjWO6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DBZQg6F</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[trustfallaccident]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stuff I send my friend to wake her up in the morning</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AAHXZYt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aRna1H6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/diErowa.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IoS668B.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ri4w7iz.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pF1oVK4.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/88BDSeG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KSVcAD8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mMo6iJt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/54hu9oM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/awxPzZt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M5ebFsU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div>